  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a libndp</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libndp</application> package provides a wrapper for IPv6
Neighbor Discovery Protocol. It also provides a tool named ndptool for
sending and receiving NDP messages.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferncia (HTTP): <ulink url="&libndp-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Transferncia (FTP): <ulink url="&libndp-download-ftp;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Soma de verificao MD5: &libndp-md5sum;
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
