    </itemizedlist>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Observaes de Usurio(a): <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/libndp"/>
    </para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de libndp</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>libndp</application> by running the following command:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr        \
            --sysconfdir=/etc    \
            --localstatedir=/var \
            --disable-static     &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

